{"tw": {"3326920": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "少女夏海和荒謬絕倫的學園", "steam_appid": 3326920, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【大綱】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>這是什麼鬼學校啊？！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/e3c7e7affbee9a1bb9523966f90b4832.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夏海在轉學的第一天就遇到各種奇怪的事情：突然就找碴的輔導老師，信仰狂熱的校長，超脫常理觀念的同學們…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一開學就面對這些過度有個性的同學與老師，她有辦法適應接下來的學校生活嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【遊玩方式】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/bdd67ffb76f3c890754c321ca31f341b.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=439 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲遊戲目標：玩家需要在20日以內將學力與體力提升到20以上！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.poster.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.webm?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.mp4?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲用上下左右操控夏海移動，並且使用Z鍵跟各種同學與老師互動吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.poster.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.webm?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.mp4?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲認真上課，增加自己的學力吧！雖然有時候可能會遇到意外而得自習...？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b75039e8bbd02e8031c532d0841d677d.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=460 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲因為這是個奇怪的學校，所以你還得跟同學切磋武藝喔！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b6ad5f1a445b607cc7b5f1f62ad4c753.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲努力活用學校的各項機能提升自己的能力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【主角介紹】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/6d0d79ef46176f25cd6085d2f16c5b90.avif?t=1762827506\" width=254 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲夏海</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平凡的女孩子，由於爸爸出國工作所以暫住在奶奶家中。<br>剛轉學到新學校，心中有些緊張。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【配角介紹】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/f4aa5b36f215c407eafb5df604b1787e.avif?t=1762827506\" width=616 height=450 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【大綱】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>這是什麼鬼學校啊？！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"